Package dkeep.logic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GameLogic
    Abstraction that allows for the game's class to save the levels without knowing the specifics of each one.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Club  
    Coordinates
    Abstraction of 2 dimensional Coordinates of all levels
    Drunken
    Abstraction of the Drunken Guard of the game.
    Dungeon
    Abstraction of the Dungeon level in game: It allows to move the hero, the guard, to pick a type of guard or for it to be randomly picked and to check the game's status
    Game
    Abstraction of the whole game and the settings around it.
    Guard
    Abstraction of the Guard of the game.
    Guard_2_ways
    Abstraction of a guard that can randomly change direction
    Hero
    Abstraction of the hero of the game.
    Keep
    Abstraction of the Keep level in game.
    Map
    Abstraction of a map.
    Ogre
    Abstraction of the Ogre of the game.
    Person
    Abstraction of a character of the game (ex: hero, guard).
    Suspicious
    Abstraction of the Suspicious Guard of the game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GameState
    Possible states of the game
